{"tid":1856283,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲老豆老母明明係偏心但又唔肯認?","createTime":"2020-02-01T14:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:16:48.000Z","uid":4686,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"2370ba45e2b7fe8d3a151976f684cd7917819524","tid":1856283,"uid":4686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"依頭比完3k家用 依頭老母就話&quot;借&quot;左3k比啊哥<br />\n十幾年啦 成日見佢成身數 老豆老母又話要慢慢教 <br />\n大佬啊 你幫佢還已經唔係教 係縱 講極都唔聽  <br />\n抽到公屋裝修埋比佢住 明明間屋有我名 <br />\n佢一蚊家用都未俾過 問我借就多到數唔到 冇錢個陣又要老母比租  <br />\n成Q日話: 你咁叻 自己搞掂啦 搵到錢咪好幸福啦 出左糧就好比家用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對住佢: 今晚番黎食飯想食咩 飲咩湯啊? 夠唔夠錢啊? 還左今期啲數未啊? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係搞到好心理不平衡 好灰 <br />\n點解乖既你就唔理 不孝個個就有你地去關心有錢有樓??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有仆街兄弟姐妹但父母永遠係對佢地好啲?"},{"pid":"f4c99e3c96141ddcc289b85f96f47004c725c3f8","tid":1856283,"uid":76563,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"你一定係女"},{"pid":"b5f9ccc4fcf72405ecb26dcd5534b76d3cc0b92b","tid":1856283,"uid":4686,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f4c99e3c96141ddcc289b85f96f47004c725c3f8","tid":1856283,"uid":76563,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"你一定係女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"出世揀錯性別<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e373328fbac20dd9929e464aee699a64200f2796","tid":1856283,"uid":76563,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"b5f9ccc4fcf72405ecb26dcd5534b76d3cc0b92b","tid":1856283,"uid":4686,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f4c99e3c96141ddcc289b85f96f47004c725c3f8","tid":1856283,"uid":76563,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"你一定係女"}